Module kivakit.microservice
Package com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.protocols.rest.openapi

Annotation Interface OpenApiIncludeMemberFromSuperType

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE) @Repeatable(com.telenav.kivakit.microservice.internal.protocols.rest.openapi.OpenApiIncludeMemberFromSuperTypeRepeater.class) public @interface OpenApiIncludeMemberFromSuperType
Indicates that a supertype (class or interface) member (method or field) should be included in the OpenAPI specification for a MicroserviceRestService
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)

      String description
      Returns:
      Description of the annotated member

    • member

      String member
      Returns:
